        <footnote id="F5">6.25% of the shares underlying the RSU vested on June 15, 2022, and the remaining shares underlying the RSU shall vest in 15 equal quarterly installments thereafter, subject to the Reporting Person's continuous employment with the Issuer on each such date.</footnote>
